				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The canonical write sequence at the end of vertical blank is $2000, $2005, $2005, or $2005, $2005, $2000. Writes to $2006, $2005, $2005, $2006, like what Disch's example does, are usually intended to change the vertical scroll <em>during</em> draw time if you're trying to do a raster split.</div>

